title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Evening' game
maintext:
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the Ohio Lottery’s “Pick 4 Evening” game were:
7-2-6-6
(seven, two, six, six)
